<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sw">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description"
        content="Angalia list ya wafungaji bora Bundesliga - Ligi Kuu ya Ujerumani kwa msimu wa <%= partials.season %>. Hawa hapa vinara wa magoli wa Bundesliga.">
    <meta property="article:modified_time" content="<%= partials.updatedAt %>">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://mkekawaleo.com<%= partials.canonical_path %>">
    <%- include('../../../../0-global/favicon.ejs') %>
    <title>Wafungaji Bora Germany <%= partials.season %> - Vinara wa Magoli Ligi Kuu Ujerumani</title>
    <%- include('../../../../0-global/style.ejs'); %>
    <%- include('../../../../0-global/google.ejs'); %>
    <%- include('../../../../0-global/fonts.ejs'); %>

    <style>
        p {
            text-align: justify !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../../../../0-global/header.ejs'); %>
    <main>
        <section class="left">
            <h1 class="fs-4 mx-2 my-4">
                Wafungaji Bora Bundesliga <%= partials.season %>. Je, Nani Atamaliza Msimu Kinara wa Magoli?
            </h1>
            <span class="meta-info-el meta-info-date d-block p-2 mb-3 text-muted" style="font-size: 12px;">
                <i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> Updated on:
                <abbr class="date published" title="<%= partials.updatedAt %>">
                    <%= new Date(partials.updatedAt).toLocaleString('en-US', {timeZone: 'Africa/Nairobi', hour: "2-digit", minute: "2-digit", weekday: "long", year: "numeric", month: "long", day: "numeric",}) %>
                </abbr>
            </span>
            <div>
                <h2 class="h2 fs-6 mb-3">Utangulizi</h2>
                <div class="utangulizi p-2 text-align-justify">
                    <p>
                        Msimu wa 2024-25 wa Bundesliga unazidi kuwa wa kusisimua huku wachezaji wakipambana kuibuka
                        mfungaji bora wa ligi na kutwaa tuzo ya kifahari ya Torjägerkanone.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Kwa miaka mingi, nyota kama Robert Lewandowski na Gerd Müller wametawala tuzo hii, kila mmoja
                        akiibuka mshindi mara saba. Tangu Lewandowski alipoondoka Bundesliga, Niclas Füllkrug na
                        Christopher Nkunku walifunga mabao 16 kila mmoja na kushiriki tuzo hiyo msimu wa 2022-23. Msimu
                        uliopita, Harry Kane aliweka rekodi kwa kufunga mabao 36, idadi ambayo imezidiwa tu na Müller,
                        na kutawazwa mfungaji bora wa Bundesliga.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Msimu huu, ushindani ni mkali zaidi huku wachezaji wengine wakijitokeza kuwania nafasi ya juu.
                        Omar Marmoush wa Eintracht Frankfurt, Ermedin Demirović wa Stuttgart, na Florian Wirtz wa Bayer
                        Leverkusen wanaonyesha makali yao katika mechi za mwanzo za msimu huu. Je, nani ataibuka
                        mfungaji bora wa Bundesliga msimu huu? Endelea kufuatilia ili kujua kinachoendelea!
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Hadi sasa, <b><%= top_scorers[0].player.name %> wa <%= top_scorers[0].statistics[0].team.name %> na
                            <%= top_scorers[1].player.name %> wa <%= top_scorers[1].statistics[0].team.name %></b> wanaongoza
                        kwa mabao ndani ya ligi hii ya Ujerumani yenye mchuano mkali sana.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="table-section" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Table">
                    <h2 class="h2 fs-6 mb-3" itemprop="about">
                        Orodha ya Wafungaji Bora (Top Goal Scorers) Bundesliga <%= partials.season %>
                    </h2>
                    <table class="table table-striped-columns">
                        <thead style="font-size: 13px !important;">
                            <th scope="col" class="text-center">#</th>
                            <th scope="col" class="fw-bold">Mchezaji</th>
                            <th scope="col" class="text-start">Timu</th>
                            <th scope="col" class="text-center">Magoli</th>
                            <th scope="col" class="text-center">Penati</th>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <% top_scorers.forEach((player, index) => { %>
                            <tr style="font-size: 12px !important;">
                                <td class="tdata text-center"><%= index+1 %>.</td>
                                <td class="tdata"><%= player.player.name %></td>
                                <td class="tdata"><%= player.statistics[0].team.name %></td>
                                <td class="tdata text-center"><%= player.statistics[0].goals.total %></td>
                                <td class="tdata text-center"><%= player.statistics[0].penalty.scored %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <% }) %>
                        </tbody>
                        <caption class="p-2 fst-italic">
                            <p>Orodha hii inasasishwa mara kwa mara kulingana na mechi za kila wiki.</p>
                            <p>Ona pia</p>
                            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush fw-bold">
                                <li class="list-group-item"><a href="/top-assists/78/2024" class="text-success text-decoration-none">Orodha ya Watoa Assist Bora Bundesliga 2024/25</a></li>
                                <li class="list-group-item"><a href="/standings/78/2024" class="text-success text-decoration-none">Msimamo Ligi Kuu ya Ujerumani - Bundesliga 2024/25</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </caption>
                    </table>
                </div>
                <br>
                <hr>
                <br>
                <%- include('../../../../0-global/somapia.ejs'); %>
            </div>
            <br><br>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('../../../../0-global/footer.ejs'); %>
    <%- include('../../../../0-global/script.ejs'); %>
    <%- include('../../../../0-global/modal-gsb.ejs'); %>

    <!-- bootstrap -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-u1OknCvxWvY5kfmNBILK2hRnQC3Pr17a+RTT6rIHI7NnikvbZlHgTPOOmMi466C8"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>